Gossifleur

Evolves At 4

Cotton Down

Passive Ability

When at least 5% max HP damage is received in a single attack, restores this Pokémon's HP and increases their movement speed by 15% for 1.5s; deals revenge damage to nearby opposing Pokémon and decreases their movement speed by 30% for 1.5s (10s CD).

35% SpA + 0 x (Level - 1) + 150

65% SpA + 0 x (Level - 1) + 165

Attack

Auto Attack

Becomes a boosted attack with every third attack, attaching a bit of cotton fluff to opposing Pokémon for 3s and then damaging them. The user and their teammates' auto attacks against targets with cotton fluff on them deal additional damage and decrease their movement speed by 20% for 1s.

Each teammate uses their own Sp. Atk to deal additional damage on targets with cotton fluff. This additional damage has an internal cooldown of 0.35s for each teammate.

100% Atk + 0 x (Level - 1) + 0

73% SpA + 6 x (Level - 1) + 120

18.25% SpA + 2 x (Level - 1) + 30

Leafage

Move 1

4.50s Ranged

The user shoots a bundle of leaves in the designated direction which explodes on the first opposing Pokémon hit or after traveling max distance, damaging opposing Pokémon in the area of effect and decreasing their movement speed by 40% for 2s.

129% SpA + 11 x (Level - 1) + 210

Leafage Upgrade Choices

Pollen Puff

5.00s Ranged

The user throws a Pollen Puff at the designated location which attaches to the nearest Pokémon within 0.5s. The Pollen Puff explodes 2s after attaching to a Pokémon, restoring the HP of the user's teammates and damaging opposing Pokémon in the area of effect.

The Pollen Puff explodes on its own after 1s with the same effects if it doesn't attach to any Pokémon within the first 0.5s of landing.

80% SpA + 5 x (Level - 1) + 155

150% SpA + 13 x (Level - 1) + 300

If the Pollen Puff attaches to a teammate, it reduces the damage that teammate receives by 15% for 2s before it explodes. If the Pollen Puff attaches to any Pokémon, opposing Pokémon that come in contact with the target receive damage over time every 0.5s before the Pollen Puff explodes.

9% SpA + 1 x (Level - 1) + 18

Leaf Tornado

9.00s Ranged

The user launches a tornado of sharp leaves in the designated direction, damaging opposing Pokémon hit by the tornado and creating a path in its wake that lasts for 4s. Teammates on the path have their movement speed increased by 55%, lingering for 1.5s after leaving the path. When the tornado reaches max distance, the tornado damages opposing Pokémon a second time.

106% SpA + 6 x (Level - 1) + 240

Applies a debuff to opposing Pokémon hit by the tornado that causes auto attacks to deal no damage for 2.5s.

Effects that only depend on auto attacks hitting and not on auto attacks dealing damge still occur.

Synthesis

Move 2

8.00s Recovery

The user uses sunlight to heal themself and teammates in the area of effect.

100% SpA + 5 x (Level - 1) + 350

Synthesis Upgrade Choices

Cotton Guard

10.50s Buff

The user grants teammates in the area of effect cotton shields for 3s. After 3s, any cotton leftover is used to restore the HP of teammates with cotton shields for 15% of the remaining shield value.

172.5% SpA + 23 x (Level - 1) + 290

Increases the movement speed of teammates in the area of effect by 30% for 2s.

Cotton Spore

6.00s Area

The user gathers spores around them for 2s, increasing their movement speed by 30% for 2s. The spores burst at the end, damaging opposing Pokémon in the area of effect, throwing them for 0.5s and decreasing their movement speed by 30% for 2s when it hits.

Cotton Cloud Crash can be used during this move, ending the move early and making the spores burst immediately.

148% SpA + 14 x (Level - 1) + 350

Increases the user's Defense and Sp. Def by 40% for 2s.

Cotton Cloud Crash

Unite Move

100s 90000 Area

Unlocks at level 9

The user becomes invincible as they float into the air for up to 3s, moving freely over obstacles and increasing their movement speed by 10% while in the air. If used again or after 3s, the user pounds the ground, restoring the HP of the user and teammates in the area of effect, damaging opposing Pokémon in the area of effect and shoving opposing Pokémon hit for 0.7s.

200% SpA + 8 x (Level - 1) + 530

306% SpA + 13 x (Level - 1) + 636

Unite Buffs (6s duration):

30% Movement Speed, 30% Max HP Shield
